---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'top-picks', text: 'Top Picks', level: 2 },
  { id: 'what-wellness-means', text: 'What Wellness Coverage Means', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'Plan Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'detailed-reviews', text: 'Detailed Reviews', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-details', text: 'What\'s Covered', level: 2 },
  { id: 'worth-it', text: 'Is It Worth It?', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Premium Insurance', href: '/best/premium-insurance' },
  { title: 'Outpatient Insurance', href: '/best/outpatient-insurance' },
  { title: 'Mental Health Insurance', href: '/best/mental-health-insurance' },
  { title: 'Bupa Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'Preventive Care Guide', href: '/guides/preventive-care' },
];

const comparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'wellness', header: 'Wellness Benefits' },
  { key: 'healthCheck', header: 'Health Checks' },
  { key: 'vaccines', header: 'Vaccinations' },
  { key: 'programs', header: 'Wellness Programs' },
];

const comparisonRows = [
  { provider: 'Bupa Global', wellness: 'Comprehensive', healthCheck: 'Annual included', vaccines: 'Covered', programs: 'Full wellness suite' },
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', wellness: 'Good', healthCheck: 'Annual included', vaccines: 'Covered', programs: 'Health coaching' },
  { provider: 'Aetna International', wellness: 'Good', healthCheck: 'Annual included', vaccines: 'Covered', programs: 'Wellness programs' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', wellness: 'Moderate', healthCheck: 'Some plans', vaccines: 'Some plans', programs: 'Limited' },
  { provider: 'IMG Global', wellness: 'Limited', healthCheck: 'Not included', vaccines: 'Limited', programs: 'Not included' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'benefit', header: 'Wellness Benefit' },
  { key: 'premium', header: 'Premium Plans' },
  { key: 'standard', header: 'Standard Plans' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { benefit: 'Annual health screening', premium: 'Comprehensive', standard: 'Basic or not included' },
  { benefit: 'Vaccinations', premium: 'Fully covered', standard: 'Varies' },
  { benefit: 'Cancer screenings', premium: 'Included', standard: 'Often included' },
  { benefit: 'Health coaching', premium: 'Included', standard: 'Not included' },
  { benefit: 'Fitness programs', premium: 'Some plans', standard: 'Not included' },
  { benefit: 'Nutrition counseling', premium: 'Often included', standard: 'Not included' },
  { benefit: 'Stress management', premium: 'Often included', standard: 'Not included' },
  { benefit: 'Second opinions', premium: 'Included', standard: 'Varies' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Best Expat Insurance with Wellness Benefits 2026"
  description="Compare international health insurance with preventive care and wellness programs. Find plans with health screenings, vaccinations, and proactive health management."
  headline="Best Expat Insurance with Wellness Benefits"
  subheadline="Prevention is better than cure. Here are the best international health plans with comprehensive wellness and preventive care benefits."
  heroImage="/images/answers/best-wellness-insurance.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  showHeroCta={false}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Plans"
  ctaButtonHref="/compare/"
>
  <h2 id="top-picks">Top Picks for Wellness Coverage</h2>
  <p>
    These insurers offer the best wellness and preventive care benefits:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌿</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Wellness Program</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Bupa Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Comprehensive wellness suite with health coaching, screenings, and proactive health management.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💪</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Health Coaching</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Strong health coaching and wellness programs with preventive care benefits.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🏥</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Executive Health</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Aetna International</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Good executive health checks and wellness programs, especially with US access.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">⚖️</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Value Wellness</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Allianz Care</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Decent wellness benefits at moderate prices, good for Europe-based expats.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="what-wellness-means">What Wellness Coverage Means</h2>
  <p>
    Wellness coverage focuses on keeping you healthy, not just treating illness:
  </p>

  <h3>Preventive Care</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Annual health screenings</li>
    <li>Cancer screenings (mammogram, colonoscopy, etc.)</li>
    <li>Vaccinations and immunizations</li>
    <li>Blood pressure and cholesterol checks</li>
    <li>Diabetes screening</li>
    <li>Vision and hearing tests</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Wellness Programs</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Health coaching</li>
    <li>Nutrition counseling</li>
    <li>Fitness and exercise programs</li>
    <li>Stress management</li>
    <li>Smoking cessation</li>
    <li>Weight management</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Why Wellness Matters for Expats</h3>
  <p>
    Living abroad makes proactive health management important:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Different healthcare systems to navigate</li>
    <li>May miss routine care without prompting</li>
    <li>Early detection catches problems before they're serious</li>
    <li>Managing health proactively reduces future costs</li>
    <li>Wellness programs provide structure and support</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Invest in Prevention"
    description="Compare plans with comprehensive wellness benefits."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="comparison-table">Wellness Coverage Comparison</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={comparisonColumns} rows={comparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h2 id="detailed-reviews">Detailed Reviews</h2>

  <h3>Bupa Global — Best Wellness Program</h3>
  <p>
    Bupa Global offers the most comprehensive wellness suite among international health insurers.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Comprehensive annual health screening</li>
    <li>Personal health assessment</li>
    <li>Health coaching and support</li>
    <li>Vaccinations fully covered</li>
    <li>Cancer screenings included</li>
    <li>Wellness programs (nutrition, fitness, stress)</li>
    <li>Second opinion services</li>
    <li>Mental health wellness support</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Premium pricing. Best wellness on top-tier plans. Worth it if you value proactive health management.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/bupa-global">Read our full Bupa Global review</a></p>

  <h3>Cigna Global — Best Health Coaching</h3>
  <p>
    Cigna Global offers strong health coaching and wellness support.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Health coaching included</li>
    <li>Annual health checks</li>
    <li>Vaccinations covered</li>
    <li>Cancer screenings</li>
    <li>Wellness programs available</li>
    <li>Telemedicine for wellness consultations</li>
    <li>Mobile app with health tracking</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Full wellness on higher-tier plans. Good value for comprehensive coverage. Strong overall package.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/cigna-global">Read our full Cigna Global review</a></p>

  <h3>Aetna International — Best Executive Health</h3>
  <p>
    Aetna International offers good executive health check programs.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Executive health assessments</li>
    <li>Comprehensive screenings</li>
    <li>Wellness programs</li>
    <li>Good US network for health checks</li>
    <li>Preventive care benefits</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Best if you want US health check access. Good overall wellness. Premium pricing with US coverage.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/aetna-international">Read our full Aetna International review</a></p>

  <h2 id="coverage-details">What's Covered</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Annual Health Screenings</h3>
  <p>
    Premium plans typically include comprehensive annual checks:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Full blood panel</li>
    <li>Cardiovascular assessment</li>
    <li>Cancer markers (age-appropriate)</li>
    <li>Physical examination</li>
    <li>Vision and hearing tests</li>
    <li>Health risk assessment</li>
    <li>Personalized recommendations</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Vaccinations</h3>
  <p>
    Travel and routine vaccinations often covered:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Annual flu vaccine</li>
    <li>Travel vaccinations (hepatitis, typhoid, etc.)</li>
    <li>COVID-19 vaccines</li>
    <li>Tetanus boosters</li>
    <li>HPV vaccine</li>
    <li>Shingles vaccine (age-appropriate)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Health Coaching</h3>
  <p>
    Personal guidance for health improvement:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>One-on-one coaching sessions</li>
    <li>Goal setting and tracking</li>
    <li>Nutrition guidance</li>
    <li>Exercise planning</li>
    <li>Stress management techniques</li>
    <li>Chronic condition management support</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Proactive About Health"
    description="Wellness benefits help you stay healthy, not just treat illness."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
  />

  <h2 id="worth-it">Is Wellness Coverage Worth It?</h2>

  <h3>The Value Proposition</h3>
  <p>
    Wellness coverage pays off through:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Early detection:</strong> Catching problems before they're expensive</li>
    <li><strong>Prevention:</strong> Avoiding illness through proactive care</li>
    <li><strong>Behavior change:</strong> Health coaching creates lasting habits</li>
    <li><strong>Peace of mind:</strong> Knowing you're monitoring your health</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>When It's Worth It</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>You're 40+ and benefit from regular screenings</li>
    <li>You have family history of certain conditions</li>
    <li>You want structure and accountability for health</li>
    <li>You value proactive health management</li>
    <li>You'll actually use the wellness programs</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>When to Skip It</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>You're young and healthy with no risk factors</li>
    <li>You can pay out-of-pocket for occasional screenings</li>
    <li>You won't use the wellness programs</li>
    <li>Premium savings matter more than wellness benefits</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>The Math</h3>
  <p>
    Wellness add-on might cost $50-100/month ($600-1,200/year). Compare to:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Comprehensive health screening: $200-500</li>
    <li>Vaccinations: $50-200</li>
    <li>Health coaching sessions: $100-200 each</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    If you use the benefits, wellness coverage often pays for itself.
  </p>

  <h2 id="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <h3>What's the difference between wellness and preventive care?</h3>
  <p>
    Preventive care (screenings, vaccinations) is a subset of wellness. Wellness is broader, including health coaching, fitness programs, stress management, and overall health optimization—not just disease prevention.
  </p>

  <h3>Are wellness benefits included or add-on?</h3>
  <p>
    Varies by insurer. Premium plans from Bupa and Cigna include comprehensive wellness. Standard plans may have basic preventive care. Lower-tier plans often exclude wellness entirely or offer it as an add-on.
  </p>

  <h3>Can I get wellness coverage with budget insurance?</h3>
  <p>
    Generally no. Budget and travel medical plans focus on illness treatment, not prevention. Wellness coverage is typically a premium feature. You'd need to pay out-of-pocket for preventive care.
  </p>

  <h3>Where can I get my annual health screening?</h3>
  <p>
    Usually at network hospitals or designated wellness centers. Premium insurers may have arrangements with executive health facilities. Your insurer can recommend locations in your area.
  </p>

  <h3>Do wellness programs include mental health?</h3>
  <p>
    Often yes. Premium wellness programs include stress management, mental health resources, and sometimes therapy access. Mental health is increasingly recognized as part of overall wellness.
  </p>

  <h3>Are all vaccinations covered?</h3>
  <p>
    Most routine and travel vaccinations are covered by plans with wellness benefits. Cosmetic vaccinations or experimental vaccines may not be. Verify specific vaccines with your insurer.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This content is for informational purposes only. Wellness benefits vary by plan tier and insurer. We are not insurance brokers. Always verify current benefits directly with insurers.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
